sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User (Browser)
    participant Router as FastAPI /receipts
    participant ReceiptSvc as receipt service
    participant OCR as ocr service
    participant LLM as llm service
    participant ExtLLM as LLM Provider
    participant Clf as classifier service
    participant Naming as naming service
    participant DB as Database (ORM)
    participant FridgeSvc as fridge service

    Note over User,FridgeSvc: Step 1 — Upload receipt image

    User->>Router: POST /receipts/scan (multipart image)
    Router->>ReceiptSvc: process_receipt(db, user, image_bytes)

    ReceiptSvc->>OCR: image_to_text(image_bytes)
    Note right of OCR: mock → demo text<br/>real → pytesseract / Vision API
    OCR-->>ReceiptSvc: raw_text

    Note over User,FridgeSvc: Step 2 — LLM extracts food items

    ReceiptSvc->>LLM: parse_receipt(raw_text)
    LLM->>ExtLLM: POST /chat/completions<br/>(extract food items only)
    ExtLLM-->>LLM: [{name, qty, unit, expiry_days}]
    LLM-->>ReceiptSvc: parsed_items[]

    Note over User,FridgeSvc: Step 3 — Classify and normalise each item

    loop for each parsed item
        ReceiptSvc->>Clf: predict_fridge_category(name)
        Note right of Clf: XGBoost on TF-IDF features<br/>keyword fallback if confidence < 0.5
        Clf-->>ReceiptSvc: FridgeCategory, confidence
        ReceiptSvc->>Naming: normalize_name(raw_name)
        Naming-->>ReceiptSvc: clean_name
    end

    Note over User,FridgeSvc: Step 4 — Save pending receipt and show confirmation list

    ReceiptSvc->>DB: INSERT Receipt(status=pending, items_json)
    DB-->>ReceiptSvc: receipt_id
    ReceiptSvc-->>Router: ReceiptOut {receipt_id, items[], status=pending}
    Router-->>User: 201 ReceiptOut (confirmation list shown)

    Note over User,FridgeSvc: Step 5 — User confirms items to add to fridge

    User->>Router: POST /receipts/{id}/confirm {item_ids:[...]}
    Router->>FridgeSvc: add_items_from_receipt(db, user, receipt, item_ids)

    loop for each confirmed item
        FridgeSvc->>DB: INSERT FridgeItem(user_id, name, qty, category, expiry_date)
    end

    FridgeSvc->>DB: UPDATE Receipt(status=confirmed)
    DB-->>FridgeSvc: ok
    FridgeSvc-->>Router: [FridgeItemOut, ...]
    Router-->>User: 200 [FridgeItemOut]
